  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649920/extras/c009cb4acd9d680a30a526d5b4d3c94a.avif?t=1763174486\" width=620 height=146 /></span><br>Coronation is developed by Twin Sword Studio with the help of Patreon and an active Discord community. It is inspired by many games such as RimWorld, Mount & Blade Bannerlord, Sims 3/4, Runescape, Anno 1404 and Civilization IV.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649920/extras/ebd51774bd8cc0aecd2189fdcee052e4.webp?t=1763174486\" width=185 height=49 /></span><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Major Overhaul</li></ul></strong>If you think that Coronation has potential, and want the game to be better and faster developed, you can join us as a Ko-Fi member or Patreon!  <br><br>You can contribute at Ko-Fi (most preferred option): <br><br>For contributors totaling $15 or more, they will be invited to join us in the MVP (Minimum Viable Product) or \"Pre-Alpha Playtest\".<br><br>If possible, please use the PayPal option as it requires lesser fees. One-time donations can be made at Ko-Fi too.<br><br>You can also contribute using Patreon at: <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649920/extras/679b035845d6b6c57d913744301d7dd6.avif?t=1763174486\" width=600 height=635 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649920/extras/c009cb4acd9d680a30a526d5b4d3c94a.avif?t=1763174486\" width=620 height=146 /></span><br>Coronation is developed by Twin Sword Studio with the help of Patreon and an active Discord community. It is inspired by many games such as RimWorld, Mount & Blade Bannerlord, Sims 3/4, Runescape, Anno 1404 and Civilization IV.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649920/extras/ebd51774bd8cc0aecd2189fdcee052e4.webp?t=1763174486\" width=185 height=49 /></span><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Major Overhaul</li></ul></strong>If you think that Coronation has potential, and want the game to be better and faster developed, you can join us as a Ko-Fi member or Patreon!  <br><br>You can contribute at Ko-Fi (most preferred option): <br><br>For contributors totaling $15 or more, they will be invited to join us in the MVP (Minimum Viable Product) or \"Pre-Alpha Playtest\".<br><br>If possible, please use the PayPal option as it requires lesser fees. One-time donations can be made at Ko-Fi too.<br><br>You can also contribute using Patreon at: <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649920/extras/679b035845d6b6c57d913744301d7dd6.avif?t=1763174486\" width=600 height=635 /></span>",
